        <ArticleTitle>Empagliflozin in Heart Failure with Preserved Ejection Fraction: A Randomized Trial.</ArticleTitle>
        <Abstract>
          <AbstractText Label="BACKGROUND">The role of SGLT2 inhibitors in HFpEF remains debated.</AbstractText>
          <AbstractText Label="METHODS">We randomized 5988 patients with HFpEF to empagliflozin or placebo.</AbstractText>
          <AbstractText Label="RESULTS">Empagliflozin reduced the composite of cardiovascular death or hospitalization (HR 0.79).</AbstractText>
          <AbstractText Label="CONCLUSIONS">Empagliflozin reduced adverse outcomes in HFpEF regardless of diabetes status.</AbstractText>
        </Abstract>
